==Honours==
{{Main|Brisbane Broncos Honours}}
* '''World Club Challenge: 2'''
::  [[1992 World Club Challenge|1992]], [[1997 World Club Championship|1997]]
* '''Premiership: 6'''
:: [[NSWRL season 1992|1992]], [[NSWRL season 1993|1993]], [[Super League (Australia) season 1997|1997]], [[NRL season 1998|1998]], [[NRL season 2000|2000]], [[NRL season 2006|2006]]
* '''Minor Premiership: 4'''
::  1992, 1997, 1998, 2000
* '''Panasonic Cup: 1'''
::  [[1989 Panasonic Cup (rugby league)|1989]]
* '''Lotto Challenge Cup: 1'''
::  [[NSWRL season 1991|1991]]
* '''Tooheys Challenge: 1'''
::  [[ARL season 1995|1995]]

The Paul Morgan Medal is awarded annually to the Brisbane Broncos' player of the year. it is named after one of the club's founders, [[Paul Morgan (rugby league)|Paul 'Porky' Morgan]].

